unsw.dungeon

Class Dungeon

  • java.lang.Object
    • unsw.dungeon.Dungeon

  • public class Dungeon
extends java.lang.Object
    A dungeon in the interactive dungeon player. A dungeon can contain many entities, each occupy a square. More than one entity can occupy the same square.
    Author:
    Robert Clifton-Everest
